headline: Hershey (HSY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Although Hershey (currently trading at $188 per share) has gained 12.3% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 27.3% return during that period. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
